<strong><h1 role="AIDE home"class="splash-title text-center"> [ AIDE ] </h1></strong>
<strong><h3 role="AIDE slogan" class="text-center"> Find the care you seek. </h3></strong>

<h4 title="AIDE slogan"class="text-center"> At AIDE, we aim to create new meaningful connections between patients and their caregivers in the following simple steps: </h4>
<br>
<div class="row">
  <div class="large-4 small-4 columns text-center">
    <h5><strong> Sign Up for an Account: </strong></h5>
  <p>
    Sign up for an account with AIDE using your email as either a <strong>Patient</strong> or a <strong>Caregiver</strong>.
  </p>
  </div>
  <div class="large-4 small-4 columns text-center">
    <h5><strong> Find a Caregiver: </strong></h5>
  <p>
    Edit your profile page and begin searching for a caregiver right for you in using our Caregiver Directory. There you can search caregivers by your healthcare needs, or filter by location or credentials.
  </p>
  </div>
  <div class="large-4 small-4 columns text-center">
    <h5><strong> Contact your Caregiver: </strong></h5>
  <p>
    Once you find a potential caregiver for you or your loved one, AIDE will contact the caregiver on your behalf with a click of a button to notify them of your interest.
  </div>
</div>
<div class="splash text-center">
<div class="row text-center">
  <div class="small-10 large-6 large-centered columns">
      <strong><h4>Get Started! Sign up for an account with us.</h4></strong>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row text-center">
  <div class="small-10 large-6 large-centered columns">
    <%= button_to "Sign Up", new_user_path, :method => :get, class: "button large", title: "sign up button" %>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
